WEBVTT

00:01.320 --> 00:02.639
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:02.719 --> 00:05.837
Haley, marry me again
in front of all our friends and our family.

00:05.920 --> 00:07.069
You know, it's actually hurt me

00:07.160 --> 00:09.310
to see what's happened
with your relationship with Dan.

00:09.400 --> 00:11.868
Uncle Cooper.
What are you doing here, man?

00:11.960 --> 00:13.518
I met this smoking-hot girl.

00:13.600 --> 00:15.079
- I'm 17.
- You gotta go.

00:15.160 --> 00:17.230
You know you still want me, Cooper.

00:21.240 --> 00:22.832
The guy shot up a school!

00:22.920 --> 00:24.797
Yo, Marcus. Would you shut up, man?

00:24.880 --> 00:26.552
I hope they fry his ass.

00:27.720 --> 00:31.633
Promise me that when you pick
the boy you're really gonna be with

00:31.720 --> 00:33.517
he's someone who you love.

00:33.600 --> 00:34.669
<i>Use your head</i>

00:34.760 --> 00:36.716
<i>and follow your heart.</i>

